location.fullValue: Kansas Plan, The Ridge At Johnstown

data.description: Welcome to 3666 Pinonwood Ct., a low-maintenance home nestled in the desirable Thompson River Ranch community in Johnstown, right outside Loveland. Step inside to an abundance of natural light, an open concept layout, and a large kitchen island. Discover a spacious loft at the top of the steps ideal for an office or recreational space. The upstairs also boasts a primary suite with an attached bathroom and a walk-in closet, as well as an additional bedroom and a full bathroom. Enjoy the convenience of an expansive laundry room on the upper level, the efficiency of a tankless water heater, and ample storage in the two car attached garage. Unwind on the private patio in the fully-fenced backyard or explore the various amenities that the Thompson River Ranch master-planned community offers - two swimming pools, a soon-to-open clubhouse with a fitness center and a community gathering space, three parks, a disc golf course, and a multitude of walking and biking trails. This home is situated in a prime location with immediate access to I-25 and the wide array of shopping and entertainment offered at Centerra. View the virtual tour for a walkthrough and fall in love with this charming home today.
